59th Drive, north side, west of 64th Street to Fresh Pond Road, showing from fore to background the T. Hallett house of 1852 and the Angelbach house. This is a set of three views.

January 1924.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

folder: Mount Olivet Crescent & 60th Avenue, Queens, NY
text:
Mount Olivet Crescent, east side, between Sixtieth Ave., and 60th Road showing Chris Aukerbauer's(?) farmhouse. C. Anglebach, who owned this property in 1873, sold it to Ernst Nurge (1924).

January 1924.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
